 
<p>
Researchers have estimated the <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/12/world/greenhouse-gas-climate-emissions-gdp-loss-us-china/index.html">economic damage caused to the world</a> by
the greenhouse gas emissions of the five main emitting countries:
United States, China, Russia, India, and Brazil: a total of 6 trillion
dollars.
<p>
With this. the rest of the world can sue these companies for damages.

 